snippet.title: Sensible Soccer 98 gameplay (PC Game, 1997)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Sensible Soccer 98, PC game produced by GT Interactive in 1997 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/sensible-soccer-98/1876/
Playing a world cup championship with Holland. Loosing first match against Belgium.
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Actua Soccer - https://youtu.be/zug1NB_zLaI
Total Soccer 2000 - https://youtu.be/27PKrCBkue8
FIFA 96 - https://youtu.be/OOo3nWSdLFI
